     Agricultural Bank of China Ltd. may overtake local rival Bank of China Ltd. on its trading debut today to become the world’s seventh-largest lender by market value, according to analysts and investors. Pershad also discusses the outlook for U.S. and European stocks. (Source: Bloomberg)  
                           

     
